{"type": "article", "id": 20688, "title": "黄铜棒和镜面材料的装饰", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-14T07:30:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606003114Kpr2X4zRnLiUPTCI.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计工作室 Elkeland 在哥本哈根的 Northmodern design fair 上带来了一组装置，试图探讨对空间感知的干扰。他们用黄铜棒和镜面材料做出了椭圆框和半圆框两种图形，再用亚麻线吊起来。两个半圆框是相互串接的，下面的一个会着风向倾斜移动。设计师认为镜面材料可以干扰人们对空间的感受，尤其是它处于倾斜的时候。这套装置很适合用来做吊灯或装饰品，有轻盈而脆弱的艺术气息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150535OzQA2W6nry0XYk9I.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1404\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150536ixyAzlNYLItw2QHV.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1404\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261505379fWM6vErKHOlehoS.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1404\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150538zOi6nEyhGwtI97Wd.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1398\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49358974\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}